相類之物，致不能安全駕駛。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/109%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c3221%2c20201130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,109,交簡,3221,20201130,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"3221","JDATE":"20201130","JTITLE":"公共危險"}